# Verification: Manual Build Process (v2 - Single File Architecture)

Because the standard `vite build` process consistently failed, I implemented a **Manual Build Strategy**. initially, this used multiple files ([src/main.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/src/main.jsx), [src/App.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/src/App.jsx)) loaded via `babel-standalone`. However, this caused a **Blank Screen** on the Android device, likely due to module loading restrictions (`import`/`export` support) within the WebView environment.

To resolve this, I refactored the build into a **Monolithic Single-File Architecture** that eliminates runtime module loading.

## Architecture V2

1.  **[dist/styles.css](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/dist/styles.css)**: Contains all CSS (consolidated from [App.css](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/src/App.css)).
2.  **[dist/app_logic.js](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/dist/app_logic.js)**: Contains **ALL** application logic in a single file.
    -   Imports (`import ...`) were removed.
    -   Global `React` and `ReactDOM` are used.
    -   Functional components ([App](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/dist/app_logic.js#828-1076), [Dashboard](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/dist/app_logic.js#355-475), [Statistics](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/dist/app_logic.js#476-547), etc.) are defined sequentially in the global scope.
    -   `ReactDOM.createRoot` is called at the end.
3.  **[dist/index.html](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/dist/index.html)**: The entry point.
    -   Loads `react.js`, `react-dom.js`, `babel.js` (UMD builds) from local `lib/`.
    -   Loads [styles.css](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/dist/styles.css).
    -   Loads [app_logic.js](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/dist/app_logic.js) via `<script type="text/babel" src="app_logic.js">`.

## Execution Status

-   **Files Created**: [dist/styles.css](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/dist/styles.css), [dist/app_logic.js](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/dist/app_logic.js), [dist/index.html](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%A7%A4%EC%9D%BC%20%EC%8A%B5%EA%B4%80/daily-habit-tracker/dist/index.html) are correctly in place.
-   **Build Process**:
    -   `npx cap copy`: Copies `dist` to Android assets.
    -   `npx cap sync android`: Updates native project (skipping iOS to avoid Windows errors).
    -   `gradlew assembleDebug`: Builds the APK.

